#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Light_Scout.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Light Scouts are prepared to infiltrate to blood elves lands and warn Altaris"
" about an upcoming war at time. Their robes are extremely ressistant to heat "
"which also helps a lot againist blood elves.\n"
"\t\n"
"Sadly, rarely they live too long in their heroic task. Usually because of "
"their high risk task they're not blessed by the ancients because that ritual "
"takes a lot of time."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_altaris_Lord_of_Earth, race=Altaris
#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Lord_of_Earth.cfg:4
msgid "Lord of Earth"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_altaris_Lord_of_Earth, race=Altaris
#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Lord_of_Earth.cfg:34
msgid ""
"In better times Lords of Earth were a pacific caste of wealthy people, but "
"when they were advised about an inminent invasion of an unknown enemy, they "
"learnt in record time how to use their spells for the upcoming war. Their "
"superior toughtness, the location where they fought for their homeland and "
"their golem servants were all determinant factors that allowed them to "
"survive what have slain over 80% of Altaris people and become legends over "
"generations."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_altaris_Mage_of_Earth, race=Altaris
#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Mage_of_Earth.cfg:4
msgid "Mage of Earth"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_altaris_Mage_of_Earth, race=Altaris
#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Mage_of_Earth.cfg:28
msgid ""
"In greater times Altaris was a prospere civilization with mages of all kinds,"
" but in an invasion of an unknown enemy almost all Altaris people been slain "
"to keep their sacred ancient's secrets. While Altaris won the war, the price "
"was almsot their entire civilization... surviving only the legendary best "
"masters of earth mages and the Ancient Keepers with the precious ancient's "
"secrets. Even after the overwhelm, surviving Altaris are procient in earth "
"magic and their multiple uses like animating golems of many materials and a "
"mysterous method to craft armors out of melting stones. "
msgstr ""

