#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Pegasus_Master.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Most skilled Pegasus riders weld divine lances that can still deal "
"devastating damage to the non living at dealing arcane damage. The lances are"
" not trust to amateur pegasus riders as these lances are not easy to craft."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_altaris_Pegasus_Rider, race=Altaris
#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Pegasus_Rider.cfg:4
msgid "Pegasus Rider"
msgstr ""

