"Somehow Altaris prevented pegasus from extinction in their homeland so they "
"can pet and ride them in battles. Pegasus Riders have an important role in "
"Altaris Army. Their main purpose is scouting from the skies and striking down"
" retreating enemies."
msgstr ""

