#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Stone_Golem.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Stone golems are the most equilibrated of all golems, while not being that "
"heavy like these golems made of heavier materials gives them some advantages "
"like better mobility.\n"
"\t\n"
"As they're made of floating rocks, they're not as solid as some other golems,"
" but this allow them to be deadly at both close and long range because they "
"can throw stones to its foes."
