#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Stone_Warrior.cfg:25
msgid ""
"Altaris people are capable to craft liquid of stones, once drying process "
"ends ressult is equipment that is harder than most metals and also good at "
"absorving magic protecting the wearer. Only maces are made with this ancester"
" method because while being very strong swords, it's not possible to sharp "
"them to become a cutting weapon and maces made of this material are weight "
"but still cheaper to craft than swords ... because required strength or hard "
"material to sharp such swords is not possible at the momment."
