#: .\units\FL_units\altaris\Truehearted.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Best ancient warriors are named truehearted and these are admired by all "
"Altiran people, fighting with them is described as a peaceful experience that"
" fills you in determination and hope. Wounds are magically regenerated if "
"being near of a truehearted for a long period of time."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_amazon_Amazon, race=amazon, gender=female
#: .\units\FL_units\amazon\Amazon.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Amazons are fierce warrios that are specialized in piercing weapons and how "
"to minimize the damage taken by piercing objects. Their bravery and boldness "
"inspire lower rank amazons to fight better."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_amazon_Black_Harpy, race=harpie, gender=female
#: .\units\FL_units\amazon\Black_Harpy.cfg:5
msgid "Black Harpy"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_amazon_Black_Harpy, race=harpie, gender=female
#: .\units\FL_units\amazon\Black_Harpy.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Black Harpies (or adult dark harpies) were the terror of Amazons before their"
" alliance, while dark harpies were being murdering in masses not the same "
"could be said about adult Black Harpies that were slaugtering amazins with "
"relatively low difficulty and enough to avoid dark harpies from extinction."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_amazon_Bowwoman, race=amazon, gender=female
#: .\units\FL_units\amazon\Bowwoman.cfg:5
msgid "Bowwoman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_amazon_Bowwoman, race=amazon, gender=female
#: .\units\FL_units\amazon\Bowwoman.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Bowwomen are the main component of Amazon army, since childhood they been "
"training with the bow for both hunting and times of war so they become "
"excepctional archers even when young."
