"Once in the peak of their carer best Amazon archers are named Bow Mistress "
"and can strike with deadly accuracy even at very long distances. While some "
"foes argues that Bow Mistresses have better accuracy than best elvish archers"
" still they do not fire as fast and as strong but still proving that with "
"very hard training you can at least defeat elvish archers in one specific "
"characteristic even when welding a bow."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_FL_amazon_Commanderess, race=amazon, gender=female
#: .\units\FL_units\amazon\Commanderess.cfg:4
